</h2>

<p>When you use the tag <code>a</code> consider adding an attribute <code>role="button"</code> to take care of availability.
</p>

<p>
    For the default appearance of a button just use class <code>.btn</code>
</p>

<div class="code-example code-example--btns">
    <div class="inline-center" data-clone>
        <a href="#" class="btn" role="button">Link</a>
        <button class="btn" type="button">Button - type button</button>
        <button class="btn" type="submit">Button - type submit</button>
        <input class="btn" type="button" value="Input - type button">
        <input class="btn" type="submit" value="Input - type submit">
        <span class="btn">Span button</span>
    </div>
    <pre lang="html"></pre>
</div>

